I'd like to personally welcome you and Maria to our Grade 4 Honors class at Think Academy! My name is teacher Omar, and I have a few important notes for you as a new family. 

1) Intake Phone Call or Form 

I have some intake questions I’d like to ask to get to know Maria better and develop a customized learning plan to help reach your goals. I would also love to answer any questions you may have for me. Please schedule a 15-minute parent-teacher phone call with me here. Note that these calls will be in English only, as I am still learning Mandarin! 

If you would prefer, you can answer these intake questions via a form linked here: https://forms.gle/citeKWa84UNa2WXb7. The form is written in English and Mandarin Chinese, and can take answers in both languages. Note that you do not need to complete the form AND schedule a phone call unless you’d prefer to do so. The questions on the form are the same ones I will ask during the call. 

2) My Contact Info 

You can reach me via 3 modes of contact: 

	Email: omar.shohoud@thethinkacademy.com 
	Think Parent app: Message me directly 
	Phone Call/SMS/WeChat/Whatsapp: +14254457108 

You may receive text messages from a different number which I use to send out mass texts, but you should use one of the methods above to contact me. Feel free to reach out anytime! Talk soon! Feedback is below.
notes: Maria is a new student, be extra warm and welcoming in the email.
